.SH STANDARDS
POSIX.1-2001, POSIX.1-2008, C99.
.PP
The C standards specify only the categories
.BR LC_ALL ,
.BR LC_COLLATE ,
.BR LC_CTYPE ,
.BR LC_MONETARY ,
.BR LC_NUMERIC ,
and
.BR LC_TIME .
POSIX.1 adds
.BR LC_MESSAGES .
The remaining categories are GNU extensions.
